{"tid":1785582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知有冇post錯台] 抗爭月曆2019","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:45:18.000Z","uid":307189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d02fc6de50cc2b84fab3a36823e47830221cdd","tid":1785582,"uid":307189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"抗爭半年，所有手足走到這一步全都不容易<br />\n每一個日子，每一個犧牲我們都未敢忘記<br />\n<br />\n我們將2019年抗爭路上的不同事件都記錄了在這本月曆之中<br />\n希望能夠提醒大家，我們是怎樣一路走來的<br />\n也提醒自己一定要繼續堅持下去<br />\n直至勝利，直到我們能在煲底下相見<br />\n<br />\n月曆中所用相片/圖畫均獲得攝影師/有關單位授權<br />\n在此再一次感謝他們的熱心和支持，真的真的，衷心感謝<br />\n<br />\n售價：港幣$100元正<br />\n扣除印刷成本($37)及郵費(約$20)後會<br />\n(如選擇義賣點取貨，則只會扣除印刷費)<br />\n<br />\n尺寸：A5<br />\n預計出貨時間：一月頭至中<br />\n<br />\n取貨方式：平郵或義賣點自取<br />\n如選擇到義賣點自取，我們將會於現貨到達後以Whats App聯絡你。<br />\n<br />\n*如有任何疑問，<br />\n歡迎Whats app 97890539 施小姐 查詢<br />\n由於我們整個團隊只有兩人<br />\n請耐心等候回覆🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n*抗爭事件眾多，如發現有任何錯漏，請見諒，亦希望你能告訴我們<br />\n<br />\n*如有任何店鋪能於月曆印刷後作為義賣點，請聯絡我們<br />\n<br />\n預售表格:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/C5mbuoQwujq3ZENb9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FC5mbuoQwujq3ZENb9&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4b0d67c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/C5mbuoQwujq3ZENb9</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHWygr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHWygr2.jpg&h=bf553af4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cs9zdH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cs9zdH.jpg&h=d39d12ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihf7kTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fihf7kTJ.jpg&h=5b1f6b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Yd8PM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Yd8PM4.jpg&h=3b09a584&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqQCH65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https